#
# HG changeset patch
# User Robert Relyea <rrelyea@redhat.com>
# Date 1587427096 25200
#      Mon Apr 20 16:58:16 2020 -0700
# Node ID 225bb39eade102eef5f3999eae04a7a16da9b330
